						"description":"Enjoyed the material? Drop a rating, it's greatly appreciated. Thanks!\r\n\r\nDescription:\r\nPBR Grass Seamless Tile texture. Single node group setup includes:\r\n\r\nThe PBR Grass Seamless Tile texture material is a stunning addition to any digital environment. With its simple node configuration and fully customizable features, this texture is a must-have for any designer or artist. With options for texture mapping, color adjustments, brightness and roughness, and metallic elements, this texture allows for endless possibilities. Texture scaling, aspect ratio adjustments, and displacement provide the perfect base for any project. Color variations and inverters allow for ultimate customization and control over the final look, while brightness and roughness settings create a dynamic and realistic appearance.",
