						"description":"Enjoyed the material? Drop a rating, it's greatly appreciated. Thanks!\r\n\r\nDescription:\r\nPBR Carpet Textile Seamless Tile texture. Single node group setup includes:\r\n\r\nTexture Mapping\r\n    * Texture Scale\r\n    * Aspect Radio\r\n    * Rotation\r\n    * Displacement\r\n  \r\nColor Adjustments\r\n    * Surface Color Variation\r\n    * Unpaint\r\n    * Color Inverter\r\n    * Others (Contrast, Gama, Hue, etc.)\r\n\r\nBrightness and Roughness\r\n    * Glowing Level\r\n    * Reflection Factor\r\n    * Falloff Strength\r\n\r\nSurface Wear / Dust\r\n    * Color\r\n    * Scale, Distortion and Detail\r\n\r\n** Pure PBR config attached **",
