						"category":"grass",
						"created":"2022-09-09T21:31:37.772677+02:00",
						"description":"The PBR grass seamless tile texture material is a game-changer in the world of digital art. This material is a stunning representation of natural grass with its fully customizable features. The texture mapping tool allows for precise adjustments to the scale, aspect ratio, and displacement of the grass. The color adjustments tool is versatile and can be used to create a range of effects, including surface color variation, unpaint, color inverter, and more. The brightness and roughness tool is perfect for creating a realistic grass effect, with its ability to adjust the glowing level, reflection factor, and falloff strength. And with the metallic tool, you can add even more depth and dimension to your grass texture, with the option to adjust rim factor and anisotropy. This material is a must-have for any digital artist looking to create breathtaking natural environments in their work.",
