						"description":"Mid\u2011poly AV setup for home theater, featuring wall\u2011mounted Legacy Silhouette speakers (left, right, and center channels), Metro XD subwoofer, and Samsung Q90 television with a 65\u2011inch diagonal. All models are optimized for visualization and interior scenes, with accurate geometry and realistic proportions. Each element includes 4K PBR textures with four maps: base color, metallic, normal, roughness. The complete set contains only 23.5k faces, making it lightweight and efficient for rendering. Suitable for architectural visualization, interior design, and showcasing AV equipment.",
