						"created":"2026-01-08T20:52:55.621414+01:00",
						"description":"A modern geometric MDF wall panel created using a fully procedural Blender shader with true displacement. The design features clean square-based forms with sharp creases and subtle surface imperfections, resembling painted or laminated MDF panels commonly used in contemporary interiors. Ideal for feature walls, decorative panels, ceilings, and architectural visualization. The material is resolution-independent and customizable, but requires proper UV mapping and Adaptive Subdivision (Cycles) to achieve accurate displacement and crisp panel detail.",
