						"description":"**Overcast Cloudy Sky**\r\n\r\nSoft cloudy sky material with smooth gradients and diffused light, suited for backgrounds, domes, and environmental lighting.\r\n\r\n- Gentle cloud blending for a natural overcast look\r\n- Even light distribution without harsh contrast\r\n- Works well for sky domes, backdrops, and reflections\r\n- Ideal for neutral lighting in outdoor scenes\r\n\r\nUsed this material? Please rate it \u2014 your feedback helps me improve future releases.",
