						"description":"\"Midnight Swirl\" captures the depth and fluidity of the ocean at night, with dark, swirling patterns in shades of deep blue and gray. The dynamic, flowing lines create a sense of movement and mystery, reminiscent of turbulent waters or swirling storm clouds. This design is perfect for projects that require a dramatic, moody, and enigmatic atmosphere, bringing a touch of the unknown and the powerful forces of nature to your design.",
