						"description":"A traditional Japanese hanging scroll material featuring eight calligraphy artworks inspired by concepts such as the Way, Love, Cherry Blossom, Beauty, Spring Breeze, the transient world, the divine dragon, and mindfulness. Designed with a washi paper texture and minimalist framing, this material is ideal for cultural or atmospheric scenes. Adjust the UVs to isolate and highlight your preferred character.",
