						"description":"This PBR texture is the Base Color (Albedo) map for a modular office ceiling. It features a grid of textured white tiles, which have a subtle, cloud-like or marbled pattern, suggesting a non-uniform surface. The most striking feature of this texture is the series of recessed square light panels that are integrated into the grid. These panels are a soft, pale blue or cyan color, which simulates the cool, white light emitted from a fluorescent or LED fixture. The color is not pure white but rather a luminous, light-emitting blue, indicating that these sections are the primary light sources in the scene.",
