						"description":"**Space Nebula Galaxy Universe**\r\n\r\nDeep space material with glowing stars and soft nebula clouds, designed for cosmic scenes, planets, and stylized sci-fi renders.\r\n\r\n- Rich purple-blue variation creates a strong galactic look\r\n- Scattered star field adds depth without overwhelming the surface\r\n- Works well for spheres, sky domes, space backdrops, and FX assets\r\n- Brings atmosphere and visual depth to sci-fi and fantasy scenes\r\n\r\nUsed this material? Please rate it \u2014 your feedback helps me improve future releases.",
